'''Shoengen Shores''' was a location on [[Brosi]]. It was to the west of [[Shoengen Delta]]. It was said that [[Randle Clanse]] was born in the rural areas north to the Shoengen Shores.

Shoengen Shores was in the influence area of the [[Brosin Underground]] around [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]].

